  "text": "### 2.3 Joint Accounts  \nTwo customers can hold one SmartSaver Account jointly. Both must:\n- Complete separate identity verification\n- Agree to joint liability (both responsible for account)\n- Pass AML screening separately\n- Have equal withdrawal rights (either can withdraw full balance)  \n---",
